name: Chibamba
description: Chibamba is a myth from southeastern Brazil of African origin. Directly to general mines. It is one of the strangest Brazilian monsters. All dressed in long banana leaves, it appears dancing in a marked and balanced rhythm. His very name, in the African language, means a kind of music.he usually snores like a pig.he doesn't like children who cry-or rather he likes them, but only as a meal. it only appears at night, but exactly where it comes from is not known. <Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>
